'''International Men's Day''' ('''IMD''') ke letsatsi la lefatshe le le itumelelwang ngwaga le ngwaga ka di 19 tsa Ngwanatsela. Lona le simolotse go itumellwa go tloga ka ngwaga wa 1992 e le kakanyo ya ga Prof Thomas Oaste, letsatsi le tsosolositwe gape ka waga wa 1999 kwa Trinidad le kwa Tobago. Mokete o moleele wa go ka itumella bonna o bitswa Malta, mme mokete wateng o simollotse ka di 7 Tlhakole 1994.<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="66"></span>


